original_title: Catwalk - Från Glada Hudik till New York
overview: Emma wants to become a fashion model and asks Pär Johansson and the Glada Hudik-theatre for help. An unattainable dream for most, especially if you have a disability. Together with a group of unusual models they begin a bewildering journey.
title: Catwalk - From Glada Hudik to New York
